  Less than two months after the launch of their first chatbot Pi, artifici=
al intelligence startup Inflection AI and CEO Mustafa Suleyman have raised =
$1.3 billion in new funding. Microsoft, Nvidia and three of tech=E2=80=99s =
most influential billionaires led the investment in the Palo Alto-based sta=
rtup launched in early 2022. LinkedIn cofounder Reid Hoffman, Microsoft cof=
ounder Bill Gates and former Google CEO Eric Schmidt all personally investe=
d, with Nvidia the sole new investor among the group. The new funding value=
s Inflection at $4 billion, according to a source with knowledge of the tra=
nsaction=E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"font-size:17px;font-weight:300;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans=
-serif;margin-top:15px;margin-bottom:15px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0p=
x;line-height:130%">  Some details of Inflection=E2=80=99s new deal with Mi=
crosoft and Nvidia are, like Suleyman=E2=80=99s iceberg, still largely out =
of view. He declined to provide a breakdown of how much of the $1.3 billion=
 raised included cash equivalents (such as computing credits) but said that=
 a =E2=80=9Cvery, very large chunk=E2=80=9D was in dollars. =E2=80=9CWe hav=
e all the cash we need to run and operate,=E2=80=9D he added=E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"font-size:17px;font-weight:300;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans=
-serif;margin-top:15px;margin-bottom:15px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0p=
x;line-height:130%">  What is clear: the round significantly deepens Inflec=
tion=E2=80=99s ties with Microsoft and Nvidia, two key partners in the AI r=
ace. Microsoft, also a major investor in OpenAI, is Inflection=E2=80=99s cl=
oud computing partner; Nvidia, meanwhile, has been working closely with Inf=
lection on the deployment of its flagship H100 graphics processing unit (GP=
U), the current gold standard for AI training and powering large language m=
odels like OpenAI=E2=80=99s GPT-3. Nvidia worked closely with Inflection an=
d service provider CoreWeave to co-develop Inflection=E2=80=99s current H10=
0 cluster; Inflection paused its own work for Nvidia to run a recent test t=
hat Nvidia announced this week had set records on eight tests of current AI=
 model training benchmarks, completing a benchmark based on GPT-3 in less t=
han 11 minutes.</p>
<p style=3D"font-size:17px;font-weight:300;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans=
-serif;margin-top:15px;margin-bottom:15px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0p=
