raining a model that took an estimated three to six months to develop, ran =
on Inflection=E2=80=99s 3,584 H100 GPUs already in service, Suleyman noted.=
 But in the wake of this funding round and partnership, Inflection=E2=80=99=
s growing horsepower is about to get a turbo-charge. Nvidia and CoreWeave (=
which helps physically deploy the GPUs) are now in the process of helping I=
nflection install many thousands more. Once fully operational, Inflection=
=E2=80=99s new cluster will run 22,000 H100s.
</p></td></tr></tbody></table>
